description:
Shorts for trails, playgrounds or exploring a lakeshores on a paddleboard. Made from a quick-drying nylon blend that has easy stretch, the Explorer Summertime shorts are ready for long days under wide-open skies.Lightweight nylon feels cool against the skin and dries quickly.DWR finish helps these shorts brush off dust from the trail and shed light rain.UPF 50+ blocks UV during long days under the sun.Dual hand pockets keep small must-haves close.Pockets have mesh lining that dries quickly.Elasticised waistband with an internal drawcord adjusts the fit to keep up with growth spurts.Name label inside.

